Apache JMeter is a performance testing tool used to simulate multiple users and measure server
response behavior.
Test Plan Steps:
1. Create Test Plan
2. Add Thread Group
3. Add HTTP Request Sampler
4. Add Assertions
5. Add Listeners

Thread Group Configuration:
• Number of Threads (Users): 10
• Ramp-Up Period: 5 seconds
• Loop Count: 1

HTTP Request Sampler Details:
• Protocol: https
• Server Name: www.makemytrip.com
• Method: GET

Assertions Used:
Response Assertion validates:
• Response Code = 200
• Response contains expected text

Listeners:
• View Results Tree
• Assertion Results
Result: Server responses are validated successfully and displayed using listeners.
